Package: scAgentKit
Type: Package
Title: LLM-Orchestrated, Auditable scRNA-seq Pipeline
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Changhao", family = "Kan",
                  email = "kch_ynu@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: End-to-end single-cell RNA-seq pipeline (QC, integration,
    dimensionality reduction, clustering, annotation, sub-annotation)
    with vision-capable LLM-driven decisions at every analyst-judgement
    step. Built on agentomicsCore, scAgentKit logs every decision with
    rationale and exports a fully reproducible R script. Distinctive
    features include cycling-cluster lineage rescue, structured
    contamination criteria for cluster annotation, hybrid (LLM +
    objective) confidence scoring, marker-citation hallucination
    validation, and per-step LLM token / cost tracking.
